<node CREATED="1568572643963" ID="ID_1252719981" MODIFIED="1568572821743" POSITION="right" TEXT="In his childhood, Albert often used to have remarkable spiritual experiences while walking in the forest. They were very hard to be captured in words. However, in his adolescence, he came across psychedelic substances and realized that they induce similar altered states of consciousness. These states are very good, because they let a person see the world differently, as oneness."/>
